video_title: Do not be afraid to spend time with your OWN THOUGHTS #mindset #positivity #motivation
transcript:
67% of men and 25% of women would rather
get shocked rather than spend 15 minutes
with their own thoughts well I think
that we are in a world of constant
stimuli and the way I like to look at

everyone else so recently I've deleted
social media from my phone like if you
go on my phone right now I don't have
any social media you know I'd go online
and I'd say well how's my last post
doing what can I do to be better and it
would turn into 2 hours a day or

like I want to bring as much of my brain
power into whatever it is I'm doing if
I'm trying to focus which will talk
about in a future chapter I need to try
to set myself up to make it as easy as
possible to focus
